content.rendered:
Directed by Suni.

Written by Suni.

Cast Ganesh(Kush). Rashmika Mandanna(Khushi). Sanjana Shetty(Sanjana). Raj Surya(Sunni). Prakash Thuminad(Doctor). Pradeep Doddaiah(Comedian) .Hampa Angadi.Pooja Bharithaya.Raghu Bhat.Ravi Bhat.Master Devanand.Charitrya Ganesh.Giri.Hanumanthe Gowda.Pavana Gowda.Hamsa.Sri Hari.Sangeetha Hegde.Hemanth.Jennifer.Sadhu Kokila.Kushi.Surya Manoharan.K.D. Mohan.Deepa Naidu.Akshay Nayak.Karthik Pattar.Protein Prabhu. Shruthi Raghunanda(Divorce girl).Raghunandhan.Raghu Ram.Salman.Sheelam.Dheeraj Shetty.Vinya Shetty.Rockline Sudhakar. Sumithra((as Sumithramma)).Raaj Surya.Vijayalakshmi Upadyaya. Vanishree((as Vani Sri)).Vishwa Vijetha

Language Kannada.

Producer M. Chandrashekar.

Production Crystal Paark Cinemas.
